Extractor

Description:
---
Extracts an information from source (node tree(s) or html or plain text)
and stores it in fields.

Input parameters:
---
* AbstractNode[]|string $sources
* array $fieldMap - a {field => search} map in order to fetch info,
where: search is the location of the fields (point for nodes or regex for html/text)

Return:
---
* array $fieldMap - a {field => value} map or multidimensional array of these maps
if a set of node trees given

Configuration:
---
* :flavor:
	* html
	* xml
	* json
	* regex